          "desc": "请输入你的登录数据。格式为：账号#密码。如果有多个账号，请使用【换行】或【&】符号隔开。例如：1iunxd0#steQXXXXXX",
          "placeholder": "账号1#密码1\n账号2#密码2"
        }
      ],
      "author": "@viyfe",
      "repo": "https://github.com/viyfe/Script",
      "icons": [
        "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lige47/QuanX-icon-rule/main/icon/04ProxySoft/pigsec.png",
        "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lige47/QuanX-icon-rule/main/icon/04ProxySoft/pigsec.png"
